    {
      "id": "39",
      "name": "推薦角色及相關資訊",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "推薦角色",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 23,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Venti_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "溫迪",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "溫迪的元素戰技倍率十分可觀，一級元素爆發更是有著將近1000%的期望倍率，該武器非常暴力地提供了高暴擊高暴傷的面板，且溫迪高頻率攻擊的元素爆發更容易觸發武器技能。在精通加強之後，溫迪輸出中的擴散傷害佔比高了許多，風傷溫迪相對而言地位有一些下降，但該武器仍然可以作為輸出型溫迪的武器，但為了減小擴散傷害上的弱勢，可以考慮增加精通詞綴的比重。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 42,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Tartaglia_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "達達利亞",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "該武器對無論是元素爆發核彈流、或是站場輸出流的達達利亞來說，都是合適的選擇。對核彈流來說，該武器完美讓該流派最重要的",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "暴擊率",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "和暴擊傷害提高；對站場輸出流來說，達達利亞不僅能穩定觸發武器特效，武器提供的",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "暴擊率",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "也能讓站場輸出傷害更穩定。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 15,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Yoimiya_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "宵宮",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "天空之翼能為宵宮提供比較平衡的雙暴面板，缺點是不能為宵宮提供元素增傷，而宵宮自身的增傷並不高，只能說是宵宮在五星武器裡的一種選擇。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Kujou Sara_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "九條裟羅",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "該武器是目前弓系武器裡白值最高的。所以該武器能使九條裟羅元素戰技的增攻效果最大化,而該武器本身也有着不錯的雙暴加成，非常適合作為副C的九條裟羅。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "弓系大部分輸出角色：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "暴擊率",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "、暴擊傷害是目前絕大部分輸出角色的數值的最大追求，該武器可以說是目前弓系大部分輸出角色的畢業武器。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "來源",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "祈願",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "奔行世間",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "神鑄賦形",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
